<L>__{exterior woods day}
<A>__{ end of may through early june, 1841 we are in a wooded area. there is a gang of slaves chopping trees into timber. it is hard, laborious work made no more easy by the sweltering heat. solomon is among them as well as sam.}
<L>__{exterior woods later}
<A>__{the slaves now load the timber onto a horse drawn wagon. again, hard work done under the ever present sun.}
